At MyMoneySpy.com we let you compare the leading independent money transfer brokers, so you can access the best rates and service available in the market.

Our technology enables you to compare FX, Money Transfer and Currency Brokers within a matter of seconds; online, on your mobile, or your tablet, to ensure you get the best deal for your money.

If you aren’t in market at the moment, be sure to check out our Daily Dose to stay on top of all the news, views and opinions that contribute to the movements within the currency markets.
